Program: Outlook
Title: Historical Chef Sally Granger
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbr2r
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
Chef Sally Granger cooks a roman feast in the studio. Also, the threat to sea-farers by modern-day pirates is discussed by Captain Peter Newton and pirate chaser, John Dalby; and, Indian brass bands and the wedding season.